name: Bank Unreconciled Transactions
query:
SELECT
    name AS `Bank Statement ID`,
    transaction_date AS `Transaction Date`,
    description AS `Statement Details`,
    deposit AS `Deposit Amount`,
    withdrawal AS `Withdrawal Amount`,
    bank_account AS `Bank Account Name`,
    bank_account_no AS `Bank Account No`
FROM
    `tabBank Statement Entry`
WHERE
    reconciled = 0;
